<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="find-fault-with">find fault (with)</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>找碴儿；抱怨；挑剔：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The fault-finder will find fault in everywhere and anytime, even in paradise!
爱挑刺的人随时随地都能挑出毛病，就算是在天堂他也不例外！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Life can be great when you are not busy finding fault with it.
如果你不忙于挑剔生活，生活可以很美好。</p><footer>2015 福建</footer></div></div>